percent of their income on child
care.

29:56.995 --> 30:00.065 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The average civilian spends 25
percent.

30:00.098 --> 30:05.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Special correspondent Kavitha
Cardoza with
our partner Education Week
traveled to North

30:05.737 --> 30:16.148 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Carolina to see what the
