30:31.296 --> 30:38.103 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: At Camp
Lejeune, North Carolina,
Marla Talley oversees the child
care centers.

30:38.136 --> 30:43.608 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARLA TALLEY: We usually see a
