deployment.

30:46.111 --> 30:50.415 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Camp Lejeune is
one of the
country's largest Marine Corps
installations,

30:50.449 --> 30:53.752 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
