31:00.559 --> 31:02.427 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
COL.

31:02.461 --> 31:04.062 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL SCALISE, U.S. Marine
Corps: Everything
that we do as Marines is linked
with readiness.

31:04.096 --> 31:05.864 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
