31:05.897 --> 31:08.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Colonel Michael
Scalise is
deputy commander.

31:08.667 --> 31:10.402 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
COL.

31:10.435 --> 31:14.673 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL SCALISE: When you think
in terms of
a Marine that is focused, he's
focused on

31:14.706 --> 31:17.776 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
training, he's focused on
deploying.

31:17.809 --> 31:21.279 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anything that he has to worry
about, from
his family's standpoint, whether
that's his

31:21.313 --> 31:26.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
