children or
spouse, deviate from that
Marine's ability

31:26.885 --> 31:27.853 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to focus.

31:27.886 --> 31:29.688 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
STAFF SGT.

31:29.721 --> 31:30.956 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KATHLEEN HARGROVE, U.S. Marine
Corps: I start
my day at 05:45 at the barracks,
which means

31:30.989 --> 31:33.225 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
