32:05.157 --> 32:10.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There were very few inspections
done of the
program, so even basic safety
and health wasn't

32:10.662 --> 32:12.430 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
protected.

32:12.464 --> 32:15.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Deborah
Phillips is a professor
of psychology at Georgetown
University.

32:15.534 --> 32:20.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEBORAH PHILLIPS: The child care
teachers
in the military, child care
centers were paid

32:20.105 --> 32:23.875 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
