collectors in the
military system.

32:23.909 --> 32:28.613 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: The dismal
state of child
care led to congressional
hearings, and eventually

32:28.647 --> 32:32.818 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
