62 percent.

32:32.851 --> 32:37.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Barbara Thompson recently
retired from the
Pentagon as director of military
family readiness.

32:37.389 --> 32:40.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA THOMPSON, Retired
Pentagon Director
of Military Family Readiness:
That was earth-shattering,

32:40.392 --> 32:43.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I would say, for those of us in
the military
child development system.

32:43.361 --> 32:47.332 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
