hire training
and curriculum specialists.

32:47.365 --> 32:53.572 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It provided federal dollars, so
that the cost
of care would be subsidized by
the federal

32:53.605 --> 32:55.373 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
government.

32:55.407 --> 32:57.943 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEBORAH PHILLIPS: People have
referred to
what happened with military
child care as

32:57.976 --> 33:04.416 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
