33:06.551 --> 33:10.422 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Federal
subsidies meant more
teachers were hired, they were
more qualified,

33:10.455 --> 33:12.657 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
