33:12.691 --> 33:18.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's no surprise, then, 97
percent of military
centers are independently
certified as high-quality,

33:18.463 --> 33:23.235 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
compared to less than 10 percent
of civilian
centers.

33:23.268 --> 33:25.203 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WOMAN: This is a loft.

33:25.237 --> 33:27.038 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I absolutely love these.

33:27.072 --> 33:31.509 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Unlike many
civilian centers,
where the focus is primarily on
health and

33:31.543 --> 33:34.512 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
