step further.

33:34.546 --> 33:36.348 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARLA TALLEY: We're in the
business of building
brains.

33:36.381 --> 33:40.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It looks like the children are
doing nothing
but playing, and that couldn't
be further

33:40.318 --> 33:42.087 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
from the truth.

33:42.120 --> 33:46.892 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the activities that they
have are all
designed to promote some portion
of that child's

33:46.925 --> 33:48.093 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
growth and development.

33:48.126 --> 33:50.762 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Even infants
have lesson
plans.

33:50.795 --> 33:51.763 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WOMAN: You want some bubbles?

33:51.796 --> 33:53.565 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We like to watch the bubbles.

33:53.598 --> 33:58.670 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It helps us work on our focusing
and tracking
skills and learning that things
are here one

