34:12.384 --> 34:15.553 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Because
teachers are paid
about a third more than their
civilian counterparts,

34:15.587 --> 34:17.956 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
there's very little turnover.

34:17.989 --> 34:20.558 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The military pays for all their
training.

34:20.592 --> 34:29.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This child care system also
focuses on the
unique needs of military
children.

34:29.134 --> 34:32.971 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
