38:51.329 --> 38:57.735 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOE WEISBERG: It's about trying
to live and
work and prosper while working
deep undercover,

38:57.769 --> 39:02.273 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
